(92050, 318959, 8025, 5, 'Hero ft. Winnie Huang', '溫哥華歌手Winnie Huang演釋，英文版〈鏡中的英雄〉。\n\n作曲：友深    op: Live a B Life Ltd\n作詞：友深    op: Live a B Life Ltd\n編曲： Dennis Law & Horace Lee@Noisyhouse Music Production\n主唱：Winnie Huang\n監製：友深', '2013-09-13 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 4, 'V1\nGandhi says to be the change you want to see\nBuddha preaches peace from within\nLennon sings with love, a lifetime souvenir \nWhat about you, what you want to hear? \n\nC1\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n\nV2\nShakespeare reminisce to be or not to be. \nChurchill says our pride is to speak up \nEverything we have, we got to give it back \nLet''s talk about you, what’s holding you back? \n\nC2\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n\nBridge\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \n\nC3\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n', '', 213, '', '友深 op: Live a B Life Ltd', '友深 op: Live a B Life Ltd', ' Live a B Life', 'Live a B life', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 16:49:42', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92051, 180459, 8028, 1, 'Action Go', '', '2014-12-19 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 4, 'A1\n(Oh My God！)\nAction！Hurry Up！\n氧氣 不夠 快速給！\n\nAction！Hurry Up！\n花俏 不夠 美麗呀！\n\nA2\nAction！Ready Go！\n活力 不夠 你甲我！\n\nAction！Ready Go！\n우산챙겨 나가려니 비그쳤어 놔！\n\nB\n快笑一個 你說好嗎? Ya Ya Ya～\n打開你的心臟 要快樂大爆炸～\n1 2 3 Boom！\n\nC1\nYa～開心都 放出來\nYa～悲傷都 收起來\nYa～跟著我 動起來\n動起 動起 動起來\n把煩惱 Get Out！\n\nC2\nOut！Out！Out！Get Out！\nOut！Out！Out！Get Out！\nOut！Out！Out！\n動起 動起 動起來\n把煩惱 Get Out！\n', '', 212, '', '', '', '', '福茂唱片LINFAIR RECORDS', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 17:02:47', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92052, 180459, 8028, 3, 'I wanna say', '', '2014-12-19 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 4, 'A1\n看著鏡子裡的我 面對面的坐\n兩個我 都不是我\n\nA2\n看著窗外的天空 像一座鳥籠\n鳥是我 你是天空\n\nB\n好想飛 不想走(飛不走)\n來不及 倒轉時空\n沒關係 還有我 對自己說\n \nC1\nAre You Ok? Are You Ok?\n我想要 聽見你說\n\nI Am Ok. I Am Ok.\n我想要 大聲的說\n\nC2\nI Wanna Say  I Wanna Say\n我知道 I Am Ok.\n(忘了誰 不會後悔) \n', '', 265, '', '', '', '', '福茂唱片LINFAIR RECORDS', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 17:07:05', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92053, 90870, 8030, 1, '無止盡的路', '', '2014-12-12 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 6, '飛翔在三萬英呎高的天空  飛離了破碎的夢\n踏上了 療癒自己的漂泊\n\n新鮮的人事物美得像泡沫  放大所有的感受\n久違了 快樂滿足的笑容\n\n走上無止盡的路 下一站是迷途 反而更輕鬆自如\n\n一個人的無助  一群人的麻木  一輩子在為誰辛苦 為何而哭\n眼前一片迷霧  旅程終將結束  放逐過後繼續忙碌 我為自己歡呼\n\n那蜿蜒的小路 背負多少重複的錯誤 我看不清楚\n那座山的高度 記載多少靈魂的抱負\n\n', '', 251, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 17:22:02', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92054, 90870, 8030, 9, '回味', '', '2014-12-12 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 6, '我走了多遠  讓我們遇見\n能夠與你肩並肩 聊天\n微涼的季節 泛黃的落葉太美\n我們飄散在風中 紛飛\n\n在燈火闌珊處 誰不曾尋覓千百度\n有幸能與你同走那一段路 \n\n一頁頁 你寫下的從前 都是珍貴\n有話還沒說完 也很唯美  美得殘缺\n像海水 回憶潮汐更迭 我好想念\n回味  輕化成一縷煙\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', '', 268, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 17:23:24', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92055, 318959, 8025, 7, 'Colors of Love ft. Sam Re C (Samuel Chung)', '作曲 :  友深     op : Live a B Life Ltd\n作詞 :  Jim Toribio\n編曲 :  Dennis Law& Horace Lee@Noisyhouse Music Production\n主唱 :  Samuel (Sam Re C) Chung\n監製：友深 ', '2013-09-13 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 0, 4, 'When the darkness fades into dawn\nWhen it''s fading like the stars at dawn\nThen I realized the day you came to me\nYou’re the love that I''ve been dreaming of \n\nA feeling I have never known\nI''ve seen faces and they shine like yours\nLoving feeling that I never can describe\nYou’re my memory that will last for a long time\nChorus\nEvery color of love gave us light\nAnd it''s shines bright through the night\nYou’re the only one that matters\nOnly one I''ve ever loved you bring joy to me\n\nWhen I feel that life is passing me by\nI just close my eyes and think you’re by my side\nAnd I’ll spend my lifetime loving you\nAnd in heaven I''ll be standing with you\nChorus \nEvery color of love gave us light\nAnd it shines bright through the night\nYou’re the only one that matters\nOnly one I''ve ever loved you bring joy to me\nEvery color of love gave us light\nAnd it shines bright through the night\nWe are here because it matters\nAnd we live because of love, you bring life to me\nBridge\nThe love that I had is true\nThe air that I breathe is you\nEvery color I am here because of you\nChorus \nEvery color of love gave us light\nAnd it shines bright through the night\nYou’re the only one that matters\nOnly one I''ve ever loved you bring joy to me\nEvery color of love gave us light\nAnd it shines bright through the night\nWe are here because it matters\nAnd we live because of love, you bring life to me\n', '', 280, '', '友深     op : Live a B Life Ltd ', 'Jim Toribio', 'Live a B life', 'Live a B life', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-20 17:41:13', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92056, 318959, 8025, 8, 'Hero  (Choir Version) ft. Winnie Huang & Marie Hui', '溫哥華歌手Winnie Huang和Marie Hui演釋，合唱英文版〈鏡中的英雄〉。\n\n作曲：友深      op: Live a B Life Ltd\n作詞：友深    op: Live a B Life Ltd\n編曲： Dennis Law & Horace Lee@Noisyhouse Music Production\n主唱：Winnie Huang & Marie Hui\n監製：友深 ', '2013-09-13 00:00:00', 2014, 19, 0, 4, 'V1\nGandhi says to be the change you want to see\nBuddha preaches peace from within\nLennon sings with love, a lifetime souvenir \nWhat about you, what you want to hear? \n\nC1\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n\nV2\nShakespeare reminisce to be or not to be. \nChurchill says our pride is to speak up \nEverything we have, we got to give it back \nLet''s talk about you, what’s holding you back? \n\nC2\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n\nBridge\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \n\nC3\nIt’s your turn to be a Hero \nFor the ones who care so much for you \nShow them you have what it takes to make it through alive \nJust believe yourself and the voices that you hear inside \nWill make us all unite.\n', '', 211, '', '友深 op: Live a B Life Ltd', '友深 op: Live a B Life Ltd', 'Live a B life', 'Live a B life', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-21 11:31:11', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92057, 318959, 8025, 6, '也許是我', '「也許是我」 (It Could Be Me) 在1996年第一屆加拿大中文電台（Fairchild Radio)舉辦的歌曲創作比賽中得到第二名。\n\n作曲 :  友深     op : Live a B Life Ltd\n作詞 :  希—哲   op : Live a B Life Ltd\n編曲 :  何崇志 \n主唱 :  Felix Wong\n監製 :  友深', '2013-09-13 00:00:00', 2014, 19, 0, 4, '又再閉上眼哼出我的歌\n無數晚心血數不清楚\n讓我去發掘真我\n從樂韻裡認識我\n音樂伴我走一生沒法分彼我\n熱切去獻唱新譜那首歌\n朋友卻苦笑罵我是傻\n話要決意喚醒我\n前路最怕是走錯\n不實際去走一生沒法子好過\n誰可自信一生不枉過\n時間沒法稍作逗留像最初\n如果盡我一切努力尋自我\n人生的寫照會是闕歌\n夜裡再悄悄哼起那首歌\n矛盾滿心裡像千把鎖\n路向要決定一個\n然後再奮力跨過\n只為會找到所想覓到真的我\n誰可自信一生不枉過\n時間沒法稍作逗留像最初\n如果盡我一切努力尋自我\n人生的寫照會是闕歌\n誰可自信一生不枉過\n時間沒法稍作逗留像最初\n如果立志堅決向上求突破\n能改寫一世際遇也許是我', '', 201, '', '友深 op : Live a B Life Ltd ', '希—哲 op : Live a B Life Ltd', 'Live a B life', 'Live a B life', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-11-21 11:54:11', '2015-03-12 14:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
